    "en": {
      "title": "One person was arrested with petrol stored in Akkaraipattu",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Akkaraipattu police raided a house in the Palamunai area on Wednesday (29) and arrested a person with 35 half liters of petrol illegally stored there, Akkaraipattu police said.",
        "Police, led by a senior crime prevention unit officer, raided a house on the afternoon of the 29th and recovered 35 half liters of petrol from the area and arrested one person."
      ],
